msgid "Dequacker"
msgstr "Dequacker"

msgid "Describe your bug to the duck…"
msgstr "Décris ton bug au canard…"

msgid "Send"
msgstr "Envoyer"

msgid "Quack! 🦆  Tell me about your bug."
msgstr "Coin ? 🦆  Parle-moi de ton bug."

msgid "Quack?"
msgstr "Coin ?"

msgid "Got a bug? Consult the duck.\nExplaining the problem is half the solution. 🦆"
msgstr "Tu as un bug ? Consulte le canard.\nExpliquer le problème, c'est déjà la moitié de la solution. 🦆"

msgid "Consult the Duck"
msgstr "Consulter le canard"

msgid "Your rubber duck is listening"
msgstr "Ton canard en caoutchouc écoute"

msgid "Quack quack! 🦆"
msgstr "Coin coin ! 🦆"

msgid "New session"
msgstr "Nouvelle session"

msgid "Main menu"
msgstr "Menu principal"

msgid "About Dequacker"
msgstr "À propos de Dequacker"

msgid "Quit"
msgstr "Quitter"

msgid "The rubber duck debugging tool.\nTalk to the duck. Quack the bug away.\nThe duck always says Quack. 🦆"
msgstr "L'outil de débogage au canard en caoutchouc.\nParle au canard. Chasse le bug à coups de coin.\nLe canard dit toujours Coin. 🦆"

msgid "You"
msgstr "Toi"

msgid "Talk to the duck — it listens.\nExplaining the problem is half the solution."
msgstr "Parle au canard — il écoute.\nExpliquer le problème, c'est déjà la moitié de la solution."

msgid "Chat Mode"
msgstr "Consulter le canard"

msgid "Encouragement"
msgstr "Encouragement"

msgid "Chat mode"
msgstr "Consultation du canard"

msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Copier"

msgid "Quack! Tell me about your bug."
msgstr "Coin ! Parle-moi de ton bug."

msgid "You're doing great"
msgstr "Tu t'en sors très bien"

msgid "Everyone gets stuck sometimes"
msgstr "Tout le monde bloque parfois"

msgid "You've solved hard problems before"
msgstr "Tu as déjà résolu des problèmes difficiles"

msgid "Take a breath — you've got this"
msgstr "Respire un coup — tu y arriveras"

msgid "You're learning with every problem"
msgstr "Tu apprends à chaque problème"

msgid "You're almost there"
msgstr "Tu y es presque"

msgid "The solution is closer than you think"
msgstr "La solution est plus proche que tu ne le penses"

msgid "Consulting the duck"
msgstr "Consultation du canard"

